mark file and select next one           «C-x»
toggle preview window                   «M-w»
increase preview window size            «M-S-w»

Vim plugin {{{1

# look for files
under current directory                 :FZF
under home directory                    :FZF ~
under /tmp and with CLI options         :FZF --reverse --info=inline /tmp

# open selected file(s)
in current window                       «Enter»
in new horizontal splits                «C-s»
in new vertical splits                  «C-v»
in new vertical tabs                    «M-S-t»
